Global Endoscopic Suction Pump Market Insights
Endoscopic Suction Pump Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Endoscopic Suction Pump Market Overview
The global endoscopic suction pump market is expected to experience significant growth, with an estimated market value of USD 345 million in 2024. This growth is driven by increasing demand for minimally invasive surgeries and technological advancements in endoscopic procedures. The adoption of these pumps in medical practices such as gastroenterology, pulmonology, and otolaryngology is anticipated to rise steadily. The market benefits from expanding healthcare infrastructure and a growing focus on improving patient outcomes through more precise and less invasive procedures. As a result, the market is projected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 7.3% from 2025 to 2030.

